"https://www.v2ex.com/u/v2xeuser", "tagline": "", "twitter": "", "created": 1443065130, "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/bf07a96ee6f886e82c49f081f87b2c25?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/bf07a96ee6f886e82c49f081f87b2c25?s=24&d=retro", "location": "", "btc": "", "id": 139641}, "last_reply_by": "Linhuai", "last_touched": 1622901007, "title": "高考马上结束了，需要送亲戚孩子笔记本，想问下现在 M1 芯片的 MacBook 能满足大学需求吗？我不是指性能。还是说最好还是买 Windows？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/781489", "created": 1622833670, "content": "大学是否有很多必须运行在 Windows 的软件？\r\n如果是的话那就没得选了\r\n\r\n能否克服？\r\n如果能克服的话还是想给他买 MacBook", "content_rendered": "<p>大学是否有很多必须运行在 Windows 的软件？\n如果是的话那就没得选了</p>\n<p>能否克服？\n如果能克服的话还是想给他买 MacBook</p>\n", "last_modified": 1622833670, "replies": 60, "id": 781489}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a4f2/3670/260_large.png?m=1621356666", "name": "security", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a4f2/3670/260_normal.png?m=1621356666", "title": "信息安全", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/security", "topics": 1184, "footer": "", "header": "我们都希望自己管理的计算机系统在运转过程中不要遇到任何安全事件。只是，这个不完美的世界的现实告诉我们：学无止境。", "title_alternative": "Security", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a4f2/3670/260_mini.png?m=1621356666", "stars": 1304, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 260, "parent_node_name": "geek"}, "member": {"username": "liuidetmks", "website": null, "github": null, "psn": null, "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e540/71e7/220603_mini.png?m=1620461549", "bio": null, "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/liuidetmks", "tagline": null, "twitter": null, "created": 1489372952, "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e540/71e7/220603_mini.png?m=1620461549", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e540/71e7/220603_mini.png?m=1620461549", "location": null, "btc": null, "id": 220603}, "last_reply_by": "janxin", "last_touched": 1622898973, "title": "由一个电子指纹锁想到的,难道指纹锁内部存储密码都是明文？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/781468", "created": 1622817285, "content": "最近买了一个销量很高的指纹锁装上了（牌子就不说了），\r\n说实话各种体验都挺好。很人性化。很赞，我都想买个蓝牙网关把它的功能都玩一玩。\r\n\r\n但是，（对，凡事就怕但是）  \r\n其中有个功能，只要你输入密码包含真实密码就能开门，是的这个是用来混淆旁观者的。  \r\n例如，你真实密码 123456，你可以输入 1234512333333331111111112345666666666 就能解锁。  \r\n对于此，我陷入了人生的大思考，  \r\n难道内部程序是吧密码直接明文存储在内存中？ 匹配的时候直接   \r\n\r\n```\r\nif (INPUTSTRING.contains(realPsw){\r\n   openTheDoor （）\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\n-- \r\n这样不是可能存在漏洞让人通过内存嗅探到密码，当然单人单户可能不值得这么去破解，如果破解这一个型号的锁，应该也是有人做的吧。\r\n\r\n如果他是加密存储的密码，如果那么验证也太飞快了吧，每个不定长子串都加密或者 Hash 匹配一次，也是很大的次数吧。（应该超过多项式复杂度了吧）\r\n\r\n\r\n我目前知道的，防止人暴力枚举的方法是[PBKDF2]([https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/PBKDF2)， 让每次尝试的时间成本很大，（当然对嵌入式设备，尤其是没插电的，可能有更省电的方式）而不是简单的程序判断错误次数超过阈值就休眠，因为这个内存中这个次数对于金手指来说是可编辑的。\r\n\r\n\r\n---\r\n我当然知道这只是一个 1000 块的东西，可是安全问题，多考虑一下也没什么问题。\r\n\r\n由于本人所知有限，有错误的话，希望大家指正，谢谢。", "content_rendered": "<p>最近买了一个销量很高的指纹锁装上了（牌子就不说了），\n说实话各种体验都挺好。很人性化。很赞，我都想买个蓝牙网关把它的功能都玩一玩。</p>\n<p>但是，（对，凡事就怕但是）<br/>\n其中有个功能，只要你输入密码包含真实密码就能开门，是的这个是用来混淆旁观者的。<br/>\n例如，你真实密码 123456，你可以输入 1234512333333331111111112345666666666 就能解锁。<br/>\n对于此，我陷入了人生的大思考，<br/>\n难道内部程序是吧密码直接明文存储在内存中？ 匹配的时候直接   </p>\n<pre><code>if (INPUTSTRING.contains(realPsw){\n   openTheDoor （）\n}\n</code></pre>\n<p>--\n这样不是可能存在漏洞让人通过内存嗅探到密码，当然单人单户可能不值得这么去破解，如果破解这一个型号的锁，应该也是有人做的吧。</p>\n<p>如果他是加密存储的密码，如果那么验证也太飞快了吧，每个不定长子串都加密或者 Hash 匹配一次，也是很大的次数吧。（应该超过多项式复杂度了吧）</p>\n<p>我目前知道的，防止人暴力枚举的方法是<a href=\"%5Bhttps://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/PBKDF2\" rel=\"nofollow\">PBKDF2</a>， 让每次尝试的时间成本很大，（当然对嵌入式设备，尤其是没插电的，可能有更省电的方式）而不是简单的程序判断错误次数超过阈值就休眠，因为这个内存中这个次数对于金手指来说是可编辑的。</p>\n<hr/>\n<p>我当然知道这只是一个 1000 块的东西，可是安全问题，多考虑一下也没什么问题。</p>\n<p>由于本人所知有限，有错误的话，希望大家指正，谢谢。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1622817285, "replies": 58, "id": 781468}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1622823231", "name": "programmer", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1622823231", "title": "程序员", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer", "topics": 44646, "footer": "", "header": "While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.", "title_alternative": "Programmer", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1622823231", "stars": 7406, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 300, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"username": "v2defy", "website": "", "github": null, "psn": null, "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/de826dfb319c26ac1d1bdcc389f91d95?s=24&d=retro", "bio": "", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/v2defy", "tagline": "", "twitter": null, "created": 1509775279, "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/de826dfb319c26ac1d1bdcc389f91d95?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/de826dfb319c26ac1d1bdcc389f91d95?s=24&d=retro", "location": "", "btc": null, "id": 264868}, "last_reply_by": "OxOzZ", "last_touched": 1622902775, "title": "TypeScript 可不可以被叫做小 Java ？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/781504", "created": 1622857055, "content": "封装，继承，多态，抽象，接口，重载，简直是一个模子里刻出来的。", "content_rendered": "<p>封装，继承，多态，抽象，接口，重载，简直是一个模子里刻出来的。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1622857055, "replies": 47, "id": 781504}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/df7f/28ac/791_large.png?m=1563424621", "name": "fe", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/df7f/28ac/791_normal.png?m=1563424621", "title": "前端开发", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/fe", "topics": 2238, "footer": "", "header": "", "title_alternative": "Frontend", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/df7f/28ac/791_mini.png?m=1563424621", "stars": 1066, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 791, "parent_node_name": "programmer"}, "member": {"username": "IdJoel", "website": "", "github": "", "psn": "", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c4e3/7418/196587_mini.png?m=1496719414", "bio": "", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/IdJoel", "tagline": "", "twitter": "", "created": 1476684551, "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c4e3/7418/196587_mini.png?m=1496719414", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c4e3/7418/196587_mini.png?m=1496719414", "location": "", "btc": "", "id": 196587}, "last_reply_by": "Ptu2sha", "last_touched": 1622902730, "title": "受不了后端同事把查询用 post 把操作用 get 怎么办", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/781539", "created": 1622869555, "content": "![swagger]( https://i.imgur.com/H5Efgsp.png)\r\n\r\n后端架构师，干了八年了，不知道怎么委婉的跟他说？\r\nv2er 一般都是怎么处理这种情况的，直接怼还是委婉的说？", "content_rendered": "<p><img alt=\"swagger\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/H5Efgsp.png\"/></p>\n<p>后端架构师，干了八年了，不知道怎么委婉的跟他说？\nv2er 一般都是怎么处理这种情况的，直接怼还是委婉的说？</p>\n", "last_modified": 1622869555, "replies": 36, "id": 781539}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b6d7/67d2/22_large.png?m=1607656854", "name": "macos", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b6d7/67d2/22_normal.png?m=1607656854", "title": "macOS", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/macos", "topics": 16653, "footer": "<a href=\"/mbp\">MacBook Pro</a> 及 <a href=\"/go/imac\">iMac</a> 等 <a href=\"/go/apple\">Apple</a> 公司设计的计算机所运行的操作系统。<a href=\"/go/idev\">iOS</a> 的基础。", "header": "The world’s most advanced desktop operating system.", "title_alternative": "macOS", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b6d7/67d2/22_mini.png?m=1607656854", "stars": 4316, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 22, "parent_node_name": "os"}, "member": {"username": "Zepp", "website": null, "github": null, "psn": null, "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/be64bc6c760278744a176e53e2af7e0a?s=24&d=retro", "bio": null, "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/Zepp", "tagline": null, "twitter": null, "created": 1500565923, "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/be64bc6c760278744a176e53e2af7e0a?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/be64bc6c760278744a176e53e2af7e0a?s=24&d=retro", "location": null, "btc": null, "id": 243364}, "last_reply_by": "yousabuk", "last_touched": 1622902838, "title": "第一次用 MBP， macOS 上的图标都这么怪的吗？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/781525", "created": 1622864566, "content": "![image.png]( https://i.loli.net/2021/06/05/TCFGSdiaj8XNWgu.png)\r\n\r\n长话短说，本来 Office 三剑客的图标都是跟 PowerPoint 一样好好的，但是被我打开过一次之后，不知为何就被加上了丑得要命的白色背景，这个有办法去除吗？要是 Chrome 和 VSCode 的也能去除就更好了。\r\n\r\n我很确定是打开一次之后才变成这样的，因为 Excel 的图标在十分钟前还是正常的，但我打开了一次后就变成图中这样了……\r\n\r\nPS：不要吐槽我拍照，公司电脑不让往外传东西。", "content_rendered": "<p><img alt=\"image.png\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/06/05/TCFGSdiaj8XNWgu.png\"/></p>\n<p>长话短说，本来 Office 三剑客的图标都是跟 PowerPoint 一样好好的，但是被我打开过一次之后，不知为何就被加上了丑得要命的白色背景，这个有办法去除吗？要是 Chrome 和 VSCode 的也能去除就更好了。</p>\n<p>我很确定是打开一次之后才变成这样的，因为 Excel 的图标在十分钟前还是正常的，但我打开了一次后就变成图中这样了……</p>\n<p>PS：不要吐槽我拍照，公司电脑不让往外传东西。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1622864566, "replies": 32, "id": 781525}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_large.png?m=1620107025", "name": "bb", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_normal.png?m=1620107025", "title": "宽带症候群", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/bb", "topics": 9438, "footer": "", "header": "网速很重要。比快更快。", "title_alternative": "Broadband Symptom Complex", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_mini.png?m=1620107025", "stars": 5005, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 108, "parent_node_name": "geek"}, "member": {"username": "wellcheng", "website": null, "github": null, "psn": null, "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c072/a096/147096_mini.png?m=1506150991", "bio": null, "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/wellcheng", "tagline": null, "twitter": null, "created": 1447465468, "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c072/a096/147096_mini.png?m=1506150991", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c072/a096/147096_mini.png?m=1506150991", "location": null, "btc": null, "id": 147096}, "last_reply_by": "x66", "last_touched": 1622902894, "title": "弱电箱到客厅两根网线，难道只能 vlan 复用吗？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/781590", "created": 1622888525, "content": "1 、弱电箱在房子中间，特别小，无法放下路由器\r\n2 、弱电箱勉强放下光猫+一个交换机\r\n3 、其他房间的网线都是从弱电箱出去，弱电箱是集中点\r\n4 、弱电箱到客厅两根网线\r\n\r\n如图 ：![网络布线图]( https://imgur.com/5LPZWpU)", "content_rendered": "<p>1 、弱电箱在房子中间，特别小，无法放下路由器\n2 、弱电箱勉强放下光猫+一个交换机\n3 、其他房间的网线都是从弱电箱出去，弱电箱是集中点\n4 、弱电箱到客厅两根网线</p>\n<p>如图 ：<img alt=\"网络布线图\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://imgur.com/5LPZWpU\"/></p>\n", "last_modified": 1622888525, "replies": 31, "id": 781590}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1622823231", "name": "programmer", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1622823231", "title": "程序员", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer", "topics": 44646, "footer": "", "header": "While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.", "title_alternative": "Programmer", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1622823231", "stars": 7406, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 300, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"username": "gzf6", "website": "", "github": "", "psn": "", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b91f/ab00/215896_mini.png?m=1487397749", "bio": "", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/gzf6", "tagline": "", "twitter": "", "created": 1487397700, "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b91f/ab00/215896_mini.png?m=1487397749", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b91f/ab00/215896_mini.png?m=1487397749", "location": "", "btc": "", "id": 215896}, "last_reply_by": "hotsymbol", "last_touched": 1622899190, "title": "HarmonyOS 的原子化理念是不是也导致应用开发的概念也需要做个转变？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/781535", "created": 1622867648, "content": "作为开发者，以后会不会更多的是以 HarmonyOS 这个系统为核心，为系统添加“功能”，而不像传统的应用开发以应用为核心？（技术讨论，粉圈勿扰）", "content_rendered": "<p>作为开发者，以后会不会更多的是以 HarmonyOS 这个系统为核心，为系统添加“功能”，而不像传统的应用开发以应用为核心？（技术讨论，粉圈勿扰）</p>\n", "last_modified": 1622867648, "replies": 30, "id": 781535}]